    {
      "id": "PopularPost184174",
      "post_content": "For God's sake, WOTC, just reprint this freaking card.  \nI know that Mark Rosewater has said Power creep isn't real and all that jazz (which is so stupid a statement it hurts), but you have a deck like Tempered Steel running around and doing major damage to people... and the deck doesn't ever even want to have to play a 4th land.  \n  \nThe point is that Stone rain has never been very good as a weak subtheme and only used at all in a fairly dedicated LD deck.  \n  \nWell... you couldn't even play such a deck nowadays.  \n  \nThanks to your stupid Titans on the high end, the other spectrum has to be ABSURDLY fast beatdown decks (or a combo deck that can win on turn 4 or whatever). A card like Stone Rain just won't ever even work at all in such a format. This would have been the perfect time to bring back Stone Rain.",
      "posted_by": "Malachorn",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost184174\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">For God's sake, WOTC, just reprint this freaking card.<br/>I know that Mark Rosewater has said Power creep isn't real and all that jazz (which is so stupid a statement it hurts), but you have a deck like Tempered Steel running around and doing major damage to people... and the deck doesn't ever even want to have to play a 4th land.<br/><br/>The point is that Stone rain has never been very good as a weak subtheme and only used at all in a fairly dedicated LD deck.<br/><br/>Well... you couldn't even play such a deck nowadays.<br/><br/>Thanks to your stupid Titans on the high end, the other spectrum has to be ABSURDLY fast beatdown decks (or a combo deck that can win on turn 4 or whatever).  A card like Stone Rain just won't ever even work at all in such a format.  This would have been the perfect time to bring back Stone Rain.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '184174'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2143\">Malachorn</span>\r\n                                (8/1/2011 8:47:15 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    R